We recommended to the management to rectify and justify the deficiencies and submit the following documents:

Revised approved list of recipients of relief goods from the source agencies (whether from the Provincial Government or from the LGU’s own funds);
Waivers for those who refused to receive the relief goods;
Authorization letters with proof of relationship for those who received via proxy;
Distribution Sheets for the canned goods, noodles and other relief goods distributed aside from the rice;
Confirmation of the recipients of goods who failed to sign the distribution sheets for the goods received;
